---
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@components/sectionhead.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy policy">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Privacy Policy</Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <div class="min-h-[calc(100vh-16rem)] flex items-center justify-center">
      <div class="mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We collect personal information you provide directly, such as:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
          <li>Name</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-4">
          This information is collected when you fill out our contact form,
          submit information through Meta Instant Forms, or interact with our
          website.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">
          How We Use Your Information
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We use your personal information for the following purposes:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
          <li>To respond to your inquiries submitted via our contact form.</li>
          <li>
            To send you email communications related to your request, which you
            can unsubscribe from at any time.
          </li>
          <li>
            To manage our marketing efforts, including through Meta's Instant
            Forms.
          </li>
          <li>
            To analyze website usage and improve our services using tools like
            Mixpanel and Meta Pixel.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">
          Analytics and Tracking Tools
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We use the following third-party tools to collect information about
          how you use our website:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
          <li>
            <strong>Mixpanel</strong>: Tracks website usage, user behavior, and
            interactions. Mixpanel collects data such as IP address, browser
            type, and usage patterns. You can review Mixpanel's privacy policy
            on their website.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Meta Pixel</strong>: Collects data on website visits and
            user interactions for analytics and advertising purposes. This helps
            us serve targeted ads via Facebook/Meta platforms. Meta's privacy
            policy governs how they handle your data.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We may also run Facebook ads and collect information through Meta
          Instant Forms. When you submit information through these services,
          their respective privacy policies also apply.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Email Communication</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          If you submit your email via our contact form, you may receive
          follow-up emails. These emails will contain relevant information, and
          you may opt out of these communications at any time by following the
          unsubscribe link in any email.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to
          fulfill the purposes described above, unless a longer retention period
          is required or permitted by law.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Data Security</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We take reasonable measures to protect the information you provide,
          but please understand that no system is completely secure. We cannot
          guarantee the absolute security of your data.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Your Rights</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
          <li>
            Opt out of receiving further emails by clicking the unsubscribe
            link.
          </li>
          <li>
            Request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal
            information.
          </li>
          <li>
            Disable tracking via Mixpanel and Meta Pixel by using browser
            privacy settings or available opt-out mechanisms.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Changes to this Policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will
          be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy,
          please <a class="underline" href="/contact/">contact us</a>.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">This policy is effective as of Oct 18, 2024.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
